n other world capitals.Read More:https://www.amny.com/news/  Modeled similarly toAsphalt Green, the nonprofit fitness organization with two locations in Manhattan.\", \"from\": 6879, \"to\": 7266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7036, \"end\": 7049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999017836719, \"rank\": 6.742175462093088e-08, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 7256, \"end\": 7265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manhattan\", \"score\": 0.8841895716918655, \"rank\": 0.13080803083581255, \"text\": \"Manhattan\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manhattan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manhattan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We would offer programs as free as possible, understanding that if you wanted a competition, there would be some fees,\\\" said Randazzo.\", \"from\": 7268, \"to\": 7403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7394, \"end\": 7402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randazzo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999849933, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Randazzo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randazzo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Randazzo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So that you can have a competitive high school swim program or a college water polo match, we'd have to work out the model to make it sustainable,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 7404, \"to\": 7562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After the pandemic, many parents have struggled to sign up their children for swimming lessons.\", \"from\": 7564, \"to\": 7659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This pool would aid in resolving this issue, providing water safety training courses and swimming lessons to children and adults in underserved communities.\", \"from\": 7660, \"to\": 7816, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence